findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward() and _getCurrentSupply() may cause OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges
findings.description: The owner has excessive privileges to change critical parameters such as tax and liquidity fees, maximum transaction amount, and fund address.
findings.function: Multiple functions (e.g., setTaxFeePercent, setLiquidityFeePercent, setMaxTxPercent, setFundAddress)

findings.title: No liquidity is locked on DXSale
findings.description: The audit report highlights that no liquidity is locked on DXSale.
